# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# Aegis private translator (Phase 7 — feature-gated optional dep)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# The rift-aegis crate is private. Never committed to the public
# repo. Mechanism: optional path dep + feature flag in src-tauri
# (see src-tauri/Cargo.toml [features] aegis).
#
# KNOWN ISSUE — DEFERRED.md D-011: cargo metadata resolution reads
# the manifest at this path even when the feature is off, so a
# fresh public clone (without this dir locally) fails gate 3
# (cargo build --workspace --locked). Local dev works because the
# crate is present locally. Do not push to origin/main until D-011
# is resolved. Fix path under planning.
/crates/rift-aegis/
